org.apache.flex.swc.dita

Interface IDITAList


  • public interface IDITAList
    An IDITAList represents the entries contained within the DITA manifest for a given SWC

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      IASDocComment getComment(IDefinition definition)
      Returns an IASDocComment for the given IDefinition we are looking for.

      Returns all of the IDITAEntry elements contained within this SWC

      Returns true if this list contains any entries

      • getComment

        IASDocComment getComment(IDefinition definition)
                         throws Exception
        Returns an IASDocComment for the given IDefinition we are looking for. This method will first check for a matching package entry based on the information in the IDefinition, and seek in appropriately. This is a convenience method for first calling getEntry, and then getComment(IDefinition)
        Parameters:
        definition - the IDefinition we are looking at
        Returns:
        an IASDocComment or null
        Throws:
        Exception - an exception if any errors occur. These can include IO errors among others
